	<p style="text-indent: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;" class="MsoNormal" align="center"> </p>
<p style="text-indent: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;" class="MsoNormal" align="center"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-language: ru;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Конспект лекций – Финансы</span></span></span></strong></p>
<p style="text-indent: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;" class="MsoNormal" align="center"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-language: ru;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
