<p style="text-indent: 18pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;" class="MsoNormal" align="left"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-fareast-language: ru;"><span style="mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; text-underline: none;"><span style="font-family: Verdana;"><span style="font-size: 9pt; color: #174899;"><span style="text-decoration: none;">1.2. Функции финансов</span></span></span></span></span></p>
